          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1690189165841-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are cooked, add the<strong> remaining chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> and <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the tray[s] and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>salt & pepper chips</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1690189169873-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
